Water disruptions will occur on Wednesday, February 1 2017 from 09:00 to 16:00. The reason for the disruption is due to two new water pipe line connections being made to the existing water system.Streets that will be influenced during this disruption are:Londoloza, Talamati, Welverdient, Lower Sabie, Tamboti, Shipandani, Nwantseni, Griyonda, Sweni, Berg-en-Dal and Skukuza streets.Please note that dangerous machinery will be utilised and trench excavations will occur. It is requested that you ensure that everyone in your household is notified about the construction and remain out of construction areas at all times.